metadata.name: Inner Reality 1
metadata.description:
A different reality beyond our own perception, where sizes are different, colors are vibrant and we are in full relaxation. An ode to the spiritual journey of the soul, where fear and worries vanish, and we are able to just be in plenitude. A reality created by ourselves, by our dream state, in pure light. 

Art made on Procreate, on iPad, by Magusz
5760px x 3240px 
Twitter and Instagram: magusz_art
Website: https://maguszart.com/
